INSERT INTO
    aqua_culture_register_species (
    delivery_point_id,till_nr,till_unit,species_fiskeridir_id,till_kap
   )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::TEXT[],$2::TEXT[],$3::TEXT[],$4::INT[],$5::DECIMAL[]
    )
        ON CONFLICT (till_nr,till_unit,species_fiskeridir_id) DO UPDATE SET till_kap = EXCLUDED.till_kap
